reviewText: 5 stars all the way! Funny AF and lots of gore for sure. A movie about the lead singers pipi lol!!
Gave this as a gift to a Gwar fan. He loved it.
My husband loves this movie and I've been looking for it for awhile. Now he has it and its exactly what he wanted!
Such a weird box for it to come in, but that's my only complaint. Good product!
